TopicTitle: Kerbal Space Program Adventures And More!

Articles.Content:
Join Nfeld and Friends for a night of laughs, arguments, and video games. Kerbal Space Program and other games will be played.

To watch go to my twitch account- Nfeld11- and watch us daily from 6:00 PM to 10:00 PM During the week, and from 4:00 PM to 11:00 PM during the weekend. All times are Eastern Standard Time.

See You There!
